extendedInfo.description: **This app is not created by Marvel , nor is it affiliated, or supported by them at all.**This is an ultimate HD and 3D Wallpapers for Spiderman Movie Characters. This application features best images in different postures, pictures,views etc. at just a click. You can set this images as wallpaper in your devices and enjoy it.About:The fictional character Spider-Man, a comic book superhero featured in Marvel Comics publications, has appeared in five films since his inception. The first film was an American made-for-television film that premiered on CBS in 1977 and was later shown theatrically overseas. It was directed by E.W. Swackhamer and starred Nicholas Hammond and Thayer David.The rights to further motion picture films based on Spider-Man were purchased in 1985 and moved through various production companies and studios, at one point having James Cameron to direct, before being secured by Sony Pictures Entertainment. Sony hired comic book fan Sam Raimi to direct three new films: Spider-Man Spider-Man 2 Spider-Man 3 The Amazing Spider-ManSpider-Man and His Amazing FriendsKeywords for this app:- Spider man- Spiderman Wallpaper- Spiderman Wallpapers- Wallpaper of spiderman- Spider-Man WallpapersThanks to users for their support.
